extends ./nus.midautumn.layout.jade

block title
  title Event

block content
  .wrapper
    .poster#poster-label
      .ps-img
        //- Replace this with the poster image found in your images/org.event folder.
        img(src="../../img/16-17/nus.midautumn/midautumn_poster.png")
        .ps-cover
    .ps-well
      .col-md-3
      .col-md-6
        h1 薯仔与莎莎的月光舞会
        h3 Mid Autumn Festival Celebration @ NUS
        a(href="https://www.facebook.com/events/289735214742410/").white.btn.btn-dark.description-btn 
          h3 #活动详情
        a(href="http://nanxialieche.blogspot.sg/2017/02/nus-amcisa-ay-201617.html").white.btn.btn-dark.events-btn             
          h3 #近期更新
        :markdown
          大家是否很怀念当年中秋赏月、提灯笼、吃月饼的日子咧？ 
          一年一度的AMCISA中秋晚会又回来啦~ 这次我们将连同马来西亚日一起庆祝。
          而今年的主题是《薯仔与莎莎的月光舞会》，以薯仔和莎莎分别代表来自马来半岛与沙巴沙拉越的大家！
          新一届AMCISA Main Comm (AMtopia)将为大家尽心准备各种美食与节目！

      .col-md-3

    .container.grey-bg.full-pg#description-label
      .row
        .col-md-3
        .col-md-6
          h1.border-bottom-light 活动详情
        .col-md-3
      .row
        .col-md-4
        .col-md-5.align-left
          h2
            span.fa.fa-fw.fa-clock-o.red &nbsp;
            | 活动日期 : 
            //- Replace the following date with event date
            | 2016 年 9 月 16 日 
          h2 
            span.fa.fa-fw.fa-calendar.yellow &nbsp;
            | 活动时间 : 
            //- Replace the following time with event time
            | 7 PM - 11 PM.
          h2
            span.fa.fa-fw.fa-building.blue &nbsp;
            | 活动地点 : 
            span.fa.fa-magic
            //- Replace the following venue with event venue 
            | PGP BBQ Pit
        .col-md-3

block script
  script(type='text/javascript').
    $(document).ready(function(){
      pageScrollTo("description");
      return false;
    })